@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### 4-1. 시나리오 준비: CREATOR 회원가입
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "query-creator-{{$uuid}}@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "name": "Query Creator",
  "role": "CREATOR"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("queryCreatorToken", response.body.data.accessToken);
%}

### 4-2. 시나리오 준비: STUDENT 회원가입
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "query-student-{{$uuid}}@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "name": "Query Student",
  "role": "STUDENT"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("queryStudentToken", response.body.data.accessToken);
%}

### 4-3. 시나리오 준비: ADMIN 회원가입
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "query-admin-{{$uuid}}@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "name": "Query Admin",
  "role": "ADMIN"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("queryAdminToken", response.body.data.accessToken);
%}

### 4-4. 시나리오 준비: Course 생성
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/courses
Authorization: Bearer {{queryCreatorToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "목록 조회 권한 시나리오 {{$timestamp}}",
  "description": "내 신청 목록과 Course별 수강생 목록을 확인합니다.",
  "price": 10000.00,
  "capacity": 5,
  "enrollmentStartAt": "2030-06-01T10:00:00",
  "enrollmentEndAt": "2030-06-10T18:00:00",
  "courseStartAt": "2030-06-15T10:00:00",
  "courseEndAt": "2030-07-15T18:00:00"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("queryScenarioCourseId", response.body.data.id);
%}

### 4-5. 시나리오 준비: Course 수동 OPEN
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/courses/{{queryScenarioCourseId}}/open
Authorization: Bearer {{queryCreatorToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "enrollmentEndAt": "2030-06-10T18:00:00"
}

### 4-6. 시나리오 준비: STUDENT 수강 신청
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/courses/{{queryScenarioCourseId}}/enrollments
Authorization: Bearer {{queryStudentToken}}

> {%
    client.global.set("queryScenarioEnrollmentId", response.body.data.id);
%}

### 4-7. 시나리오 준비: 결제 확정
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/enrollments/{{queryScenarioEnrollmentId}}/confirm-payment
Authorization: Bearer {{queryStudentToken}}

### 4-8. STUDENT가 내 수강 신청 목록 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/me/enrollments?page=1&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{queryStudentToken}}

### 4-9. ADMIN이 Course별 수강생 목록 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/courses/{{queryScenarioCourseId}}/students?page=1&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{queryAdminToken}}

### 4-10. CREATOR가 본인 Course 수강생 목록 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/courses/{{queryScenarioCourseId}}/students?page=1&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{queryCreatorToken}}

### 4-11. STUDENT가 Course별 수강생 목록 조회 시도: 403 기대
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/courses/{{queryScenarioCourseId}}/students?page=1&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{queryStudentToken}}
